{"title":"POC Omne Beacon Adds Integrated Light Visibility to Versatile Helmet Family","link":"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-beacon-helmet-with-integrated-led-taillight/","date":1698960254000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1067\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>POC’s Omne Beacon with integrated taillight is the latest boosted safety addition to their most versatile Omne road, gravel &amp; commuter bike family. The latest evolution in POC’s ‘whole helmet’ safety concept to “<em>give riders even more security and visibility in dark and low-light conditions, the Omne Beacon integrates a rechargeable LED rear light and additional reflective details</em>“.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight, blinking red light\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_blinkie-light-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/POC)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Adding an integrated rechargeable LED taillight to a helmet isn’t all that new of an idea. But what POC is doing, is continuing to refine rider visibility in subtle ways that make it easier to be safer on the road. You still get all the benefits of the original Omne Air, just with an extra lit Beacon on the back. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And the runtime that little blinking taillight is more than 30 hours on a single charge.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight, rear blinkie light\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_bright-rear-light-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The light itself is a set of 4 bright LEDs outputting a max of 32 lumens in the brightest Vivid mode. Dial it back to Steady mode of Blinking mode with 24 lumens of light output and longer runtimes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vivid will run around 13hr at that max output. Steady delivers 17hr, while Blinging will go for approximately 32hr of riding in low-light conditions. Then, recharge it via SUB-C in about 4hr back to full capacity.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight, side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-side-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The semi-aero vented POC Omne Beacon is a standard in-mold EPS helmet with a polycarbonate shell. Add inside of that a MIPS Integra system for light, seamless additional rotational impact protection. Then a 360° dial adjust system lets you dial in a comfortable, secure fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight, front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_green-front-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Omne Beacon is certified to EN 1078, CPSC 1203 &amp; AS/NZS 2063 safety standards for global use. Its internal electronics meet CE certifications, and are IP55 rated to resist regular dust and water infiltration.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Other Omne family helmets</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Ultra MIPS bikepacking gravel bike helmet with strap-on adventure cargo mounts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Ultra-MIPS-bikepacking-gravel-bike-helmet-with-strap-on-adventure-cargo-mounts-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>POC Omne Ultra</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Lite lightweight road &amp; gravel bike helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet-800x600.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2023-POC-Omne-Lite-lightweight-road-gravel-bike-helmet-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>Omne Lite</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight.jpg\"><img width=\"1200\" height=\"1600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Eternal solar-powered light aero road &amp; gravel bike helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight-225x300.jpg 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight-90x120.jpg 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-OMNE-Eternal_solar-powered-helmet-with-forever-LED-taillight-1152x1536.jpg 1152w\" /></a><figcaption>POC Omne Eternal</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Air Resistance MIPS light aero gravel bike helmet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/POC-Omne-Air-Resistance-MIPS_gravel-bike-helmet-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>Omne Air Resistance MIPS</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large.jpeg\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Omne Air MIPS helmet in white and orange\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/10770_Omne-Air-MIPS_1217_FluorescentOrangeAVIP_0001-Large-768x768.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>POC Omne Air</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The broad Omne family also includes several other unique helmets, like: The bikepacking adventure-ready <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-ultra-helmet-straps-on-adventure-mounts-while-omne-lite-gets-20-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">Omne Ultra</a> with its strap-on attachments. The 20% lighter <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-ultra-helmet-straps-on-adventure-mounts-while-omne-lite-gets-20-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">Omne Lite</a> for hotter weather riding. The solar-powered <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-eternal-solar-powered-helmet-powers-built-in-lights-for-endless-visibility/\" target=\"_blank\">Omne Eternal</a> with lights you’ll never have to recharge. The on &amp; off-road <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-air-resistance-spin-adds-multi-purpose-protection-on-or-off-road/\" target=\"_blank\">Omne Air Resistance</a> with a cute little peak. And the OG, original <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-brings-out-2019-road-mtb-clothing-helmets-protective-gear/\" target=\"_blank\">Omne Air</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>POC Omne Beacon – Pricing, options  &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"750\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options.jpg\" alt=\"POC Omne Beacon helmet with integrated LED taillight, MIPS AVIP colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options-297x111.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options-800x300.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options-120x45.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options-768x288.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/POC-Omne-Beacon-helmet-with-integrated-LED-taillight_AVIP-color-options-1536x576.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>POC Omne Beacon AVIP MIPS</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new POC Omne Beacon sells for $240 / 240€ and is available in three sizes. Size S (50-56cm) has a claimed weight of 320g;  M (54-59cm) at 330g; and L (56-61cm) at 390g – all claimed with integrated electronics. Get them starting this month direct from POC or regular retailers in three hi-viz AVIP color ways. Pick from matte Uranium Black, shiny Hydrogen White, or matte Epidote Green. All with an AVIP Fluorescent Orange back rear, the built-in light, and reflective detailing.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.pocsports.com/\" target=\"_blank\">POCsports.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/poc-omne-beacon-helmet-with-integrated-led-taillight/\">POC Omne Beacon Adds Integrated Light Visibility to Versatile Helmet Family</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f2859746782bd8d7331a5151dc91ff4ee3daa7cc8c48c580ce0aed97ddbb49cc","category":"Cycling"}